GSO Capital Partners (Private Equity)

                    GSO Capital Partners' private equity activities focus on mezzanine financings. The firm's mezzanine investment strategy targets investments in upper middle-market companies with earnings of $25 million to $200 million. The GSO Capital Opportunities Fund invests in first- and second-lien loans, mezzanine debt, high-yield debt, structured equity and private equity.                  




