                    Prior - 2015                  


PJT Partners, Inc.

                    PJT Partners, Inc. engages in the provision of strategic advisory, restructuring and reorganization, and funds advisory services to corporations, financial sponsors, institutional investors, and governments. It also involves in fund placement and secondary advisory services for alternative investment managers. The company was founded in October 2015 and is headquartered in New York, NY.                  




Chairman, Board of Directors

                    Prior                  


Blackstone Distressed Securities Advisors LP

                    Blackstone Distressed Securities Advisors invests primarily in distressed and defaulted debt securities and related equities, with an emphasis on smaller, less efficiently traded issues. They invest in leveraged loans, second lien loans, high yield bonds, distressed securities, mezzanine securities, public and private equity, and credit derivatives.The firm's investment process uses a variety of proprietary and non-proprietary research models as well as third-party reports and in-house analysis, and tends to follow a bottom-up approach.They conduct an in-depth review of potential investments through 1) analysis of corporate activities and financials, 2) reviews of annual reports, prospectuses and other filings, and 3) meetings with senior management of their target companies.The firm seeks to capitalize on both long- and short-term inefficiencies in the market. They also occasionally invest opportunistically seeking short-term gains, and may weight their strategy towards deep value.                  




